02:33:31.366 --> 02:33:33.143
LIAM: Scanlan, Vex.

02:33:33.143 --> 02:33:39.303
ASHLEY: I'm going to cast the thing on him.

02:33:39.303 --> 02:33:48.319
MATT: Okay, so you cast Thaumaturgy on him to give
