MATT: Make a persuasion check.

02:38:43.888 --> 02:38:46.156
MARISHA: Get it. Get it. Get it.

02:38:46.156 --> 02:38:50.055
LIAM: Yep. Yep yep yep yep. Vax is quietly moving
